      "title": "Treasure Chest",
      "pageid": 3232,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Treasure Chest</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Treasure_Chest.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Treasure Chest.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/32/Treasure_Chest.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">Wow, it's loaded with treasure! This is sure to fetch a good price.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><ul><li><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Artifact Trove.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Artifact_Trove.png/24px-Artifact_Trove.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Artifact_Trove.png/36px-Artifact_Trove.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/82/Artifact_Trove.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Artifact_Trove\" title=\"Artifact Trove\">Artifact Trove</a>&#160;(3.7%)</span></li><li><a href=\"/SquidFest\" title=\"SquidFest\">SquidFest</a> festival</li><li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Fishing Treasure Chest.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/bb/Fishing_Treasure_Chest.png/24px-Fishing_Treasure_Chest.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/bb/Fishing_Treasure_Chest.png/36px-Fishing_Treasure_Chest.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/bb/Fishing_Treasure_Chest.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Fishing#Treasure_Chests\" title=\"Fishing\">Fishing Treasure Chest</a>&#160;(0.24%)</span></li><li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Secret Note.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ec/Secret_Note.png/24px-Secret_Note.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ec/Secret_Note.png/36px-Secret_Note.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ec/Secret_Note.png/48px-Secret_Note.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Secret_Notes#Secret_Note_.2316\" title=\"Secret Notes\">Secret Note #16</a></span></li><li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Spook Fish.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8c/Spook_Fish.png/24px-Spook_Fish.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8c/Spook_Fish.png/36px-Spook_Fish.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8c/Spook_Fish.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Spook_Fish\" title=\"Spook Fish\">Spook Fish</a>&#160;(<a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>)</span> (0.3%)</li></ul></td>\n\t</tr> \n\t<tr>\n\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Sell Price</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"5000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />5,000g</span>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<dl><dd><i>For the treasure chests obtainable while fishing, see <a href=\"/Fishing#Treasure_Chests\" title=\"Fishing\">Fishing#Treasure Chests</a>.</i></dd></dl>\n<p>The <b>Treasure Chest</b> is a special item that can be obtained in several ways.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Locations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Locations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Gifting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gifting</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Bundles\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bundles</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Tailoring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tailoring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quests\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quests</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Locations\">Locations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Treasure_Chest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Locations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Treasure chests can be found from the following sources:\n</p>\n<ul><li>0.24% chance from a <a href=\"/Fishing#Treasure_Chests\" title=\"Fishing\">Fishing Treasure Chest</a> after reaching <a href=\"/Fishing#Fishing_Skill\" title=\"Fishing\">Fishing level 2</a>.</li>\n<li>3.7% chance from an <a href=\"/Artifact_Trove\" title=\"Artifact Trove\">Artifact Trove</a>.</li>\n<li>0.8% chance from a <a href=\"/Mystery_Box\" title=\"Mystery Box\">Mystery Box</a>.</li>\n<li>1.57% chance from a <a href=\"/Golden_Mystery_Box\" title=\"Golden Mystery Box\">Golden Mystery Box</a>.</li>\n<li>0.3% chance from a <a href=\"/Spook_Fish\" title=\"Spook Fish\">Spook Fish</a> <a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a> with a population of at least 9.</li>\n<li>One after finding <a href=\"/Secret_Notes#Secret_Note_.2316\" title=\"Secret Notes\">Secret Note #16</a> and <a href=\"/Hoes\" title=\"Hoes\">digging</a> at the red \"X\" depicted in the note.</li>\n<li>Received as a guaranteed gold tier reward on the 13th of Winter for the <a href=\"/SquidFest\" title=\"SquidFest\">SquidFest</a> festival.</li>\n<li>Randomly obtained from the <a href=\"/Mayor%27s_Manor#Prize_Machine\" title=\"Mayor&#39;s Manor\">prize machine</a> in the <a href=\"/Mayor%27s_Manor\" title=\"Mayor&#39;s Manor\">Mayor's Manor</a> after the player has received 22 prizes.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gifting\">Gifting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Treasure_Chest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Gifting\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Villager Reactions\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Like\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\"><img alt=\"Abigail Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/63/Abigail_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\">Abigail</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\"><img alt=\"Alex Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Alex_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\">Alex</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Caroline\" title=\"Caroline\"><img alt=\"Caroline Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Caroline_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Caroline\" title=\"Caroline\">Caroline</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Clint\" title=\"Clint\"><img alt=\"Clint Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/74/Clint_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Clint\" title=\"Clint\">Clint</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Demetrius\" title=\"Demetrius\"><img alt=\"Demetrius Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Demetrius_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Demetrius\" title=\"Demetrius\">Demetrius</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\"><img alt=\"Dwarf Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/08/Dwarf_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">Dwarf</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Elliott\" title=\"Elliott\"><img alt=\"Elliott Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6f/Elliott_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Elliott\" title=\"Elliott\">Elliott</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\"><img alt=\"Emily Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c3/Emily_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Evelyn\" title=\"Evelyn\"><img alt=\"Evelyn Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/54/Evelyn_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Evelyn\" title=\"Evelyn\">Evelyn</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/George\" title=\"George\"><img alt=\"George Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/ad/George_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/George\" title=\"George\">George</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Gus\" title=\"Gus\"><img alt=\"Gus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Gus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Gus\" title=\"Gus\">Gus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\"><img alt=\"Haley Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Haley_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\"><img alt=\"Harvey Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7a/Harvey_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Harvey\" title=\"Harvey\">Harvey</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\"><img alt=\"Jas Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/68/Jas_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\"><img alt=\"Jodi Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Jodi_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\">Jodi</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\"><img alt=\"Kent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/8/86/Kent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\">Kent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\"><img alt=\"Krobus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/10/Krobus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\"><img alt=\"Leah Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6e/Leah_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\">Leah</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\"><img alt=\"Leo Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3d/Leo_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\">Leo</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\"><img alt=\"Lewis Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Lewis_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\"><img alt=\"Marnie Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Marnie_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\"><img alt=\"Maru Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Maru_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\">Maru</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\"><img alt=\"Pam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Pam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\"><img alt=\"Penny Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/bc/Penny_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\"><img alt=\"Pierre Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/cf/Pierre_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\">Pierre</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\"><img alt=\"Robin Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d1/Robin_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Dislike\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\"><img alt=\"Linus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Linus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Treasure_Chest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Treasure Chest is not used in any <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">bundles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Treasure_Chest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Treasure Chest is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Pirate Hat.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/Pirate_Hat.png/24px-Pirate_Hat.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/Pirate_Hat.png/36px-Pirate_Hat.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/Pirate_Hat.png/48px-Pirate_Hat.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Pirate_Hat\" title=\"Pirate Hat\">Pirate Hat</a></span>. It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Treasure_Chest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Treasure Chest is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Treasure_Chest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>If a Treasure Chest is gifted to <a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a>, he will not accept the gift and will give it back to the player.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Treasure_Chest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.3.27\" title=\"Version History\">1.3.27</a>: Can be obtained after finding <a href=\"/Secret_Notes#Secret_Note_.2316\" title=\"Secret Notes\">Secret Note #16</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Added <a href=\"/Artifact_Trove\" title=\"Artifact Trove\">Artifact Trove</a> as a source. Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>. Can be produced by Fish Ponds.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Now a prize for the <a href=\"/SquidFest\" title=\"SquidFest\">SquidFest</a> festival. Added as possible prize from <a href=\"/Mystery_Box\" title=\"Mystery Box\">Mystery Boxes</a> and <a href=\"/Golden_Mystery_Box\" title=\"Golden Mystery Box\">Golden Mystery Boxes</a>. No longer a universally hated gift; is now disliked by Linus and liked by everyone else. Can now be obtained from the <a href=\"/Mayor%27s_Manor#Prize_Machine\" title=\"Mayor&#39;s Manor\">prize machine</a>. Can now be used as decoration in <a href=\"/Fish_Tank\" title=\"Fish Tank\">Fish Tanks</a>.</li></ul>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414153715\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.106 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.123 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1344/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16972/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2885/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1880/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.003/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 565 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   55.740      1 -total\n 67.99%   37.898      1 Template:Infobox\n 23.24%   12.956      1 Template:Description\n 22.67%   12.637      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 21.36%   11.905      5 Template:Name\n  6.16%    3.436      4 Template:History\n  3.71%    2.069      2 Template:Price\n  3.23%    1.802      4 Template:Version\n  2.14%    1.192      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:3232-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414153715 and revision id 187298\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng       = Treasure Chest\n|source    = <ul><li>{{name|Artifact Trove|3.7%}}</li><li>[[SquidFest]] festival</li><li>{{name|Fishing Treasure Chest|0.24%}}</li><li>{{name|Secret Note|link=Secret Notes#Secret Note #16{{!}}Secret Note #16}}</li><li>{{name|Spook Fish|[[Fish Pond]]|class=inline}} (0.3%)</li></ul>\n|sellprice = 5000\n|quality   = false\n}}\n:''For the treasure chests obtainable while fishing, see [[Fishing#Treasure Chests]].''\n\nThe '''Treasure Chest''' is a special item that can be obtained in several ways.\n\n==Locations==\nTreasure chests can be found from the following sources:\n*0.24% chance from a [[Fishing#Treasure Chests|Fishing Treasure Chest]] after reaching [[Fishing#Fishing Skill|Fishing level 2]].\n*3.7% chance from an [[Artifact Trove]]. \n*0.8% chance from a [[Mystery Box]].\n*1.57% chance from a [[Golden Mystery Box]].\n*0.3% chance from a [[Spook Fish]] [[Fish Pond]] with a population of at least 9.\n*One after finding [[Secret Notes#Secret Note #16|Secret Note #16]] and [[Hoes|digging]] at the red \"X\" depicted in the note.\n*Received as a guaranteed gold tier reward on the 13th of Winter for the [[SquidFest]] festival.\n*Randomly obtained from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|prize machine]] in the [[Mayor's Manor]] after the player has received 22 prizes.\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Leo,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n|dislike=Linus\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nThe Treasure Chest is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nThe Treasure Chest is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the {{name|Pirate Hat|class=inline}}. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\nThe Treasure Chest is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==Trivia==\n* If a Treasure Chest is gifted to [[Linus]], he will not accept the gift and will give it back to the player.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.3.27|Can be obtained after finding [[Secret Notes#Secret Note #16|Secret Note #16]].}}\n{{History|1.4|Added [[Artifact Trove]] as a source. Can now be used in [[Tailoring]]. Can be produced by Fish Ponds.}}\n{{History|1.6|Now a prize for the [[SquidFest]] festival. Added as possible prize from [[Mystery Box]]es and [[Golden Mystery Box]]es. No longer a universally hated gift; is now disliked by Linus and liked by everyone else. Can now be obtained from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|prize machine]]. Can now be used as decoration in [[Fish Tank]]s.}}\n\n[[Category:Fishing]]\n[[Category:Special items]]\n\n[[de:Schatzkiste]]\n[[es:Cofre del tesoro]]\n[[fr:Coffre au trésor]]\n[[it:Scrigno del tesoro]]\n[[ja:宝箱]]\n[[ko:보물상자]]\n[[hu:Kincses láda]]\n[[pt:Baú do tesouro]]\n[[ru:Сундук с сокровищами]]\n[[tr:Hazine Sandığı]]\n[[zh:财宝箱]]"
